            "title": "Subcompartments of the macrophage recycling endosome direct the differential secretion of IL-6 and TNF??",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Anthony P.",
                    "lastName": "Manderson"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
